---
title: Tofu Noodles in Peanut Sauce with carrot and bell pepper
description: This peanut-based dish features crispy tofu, meaning it's packed with protein. The tender veg provides added vitamins and minerals for a nutritious, quick and satisfying stir-fry.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W47_IE_IEVV18757-2_Main__1high-eaeedf03.jpg
